queries.query: SELECT  {id_name} as id_value, '{object_type}' as id_type, '{id_name}' as id_name, '{id_source}' as id_source FROM {object_type} WHERE {id_name} = {id_value}

SELECT '{id_name}' as id_name, '{id_type}' as id_type, '{id_source}' as id_source, changelogdetail_id as detail_id, changelog_id, data_dict_id, detail1_value as detail_one_value, detail1 as detail_one, detail2 as detail_two FROM ChangeLogDetail WHERE changelogdetail_id = {id_value}

SELECT cl.change_date_utc, cl.client_id, cl.clientvisit_id, cl.emp_id, cl.record_id, ct.record_type, ct.primarykey_name FROM ChangeLog as cl INNER JOIN ChangeLogDetail as cd ON cl.changelog_id = cd.changelog_id INNER JOIN ChangeLogType as ct ON cl.changelogtype_id = ct.changelogtype_id WHERE cd.changelogdetail_id = {id_value}

SELECT '{id_name}' as id_name, '{id_type}' as id_type, '{id_source}' as id_source, cl.changelog_id, ct.description as change_description, cl.change_date, cl.change_date_utc FROM ChangeLog as cl LEFT OUTER JOIN ChangeLogType as ct ON cl.changelogtype_id = ct.changelogtype_id LEFT OUTER JOIN ChangeLogDetail as cd ON cl.changelog_id = cd.changelog_id WHERE cl.changelog_id = {id_value}
